WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.020
Okay, go to sleep.

2
00:00:02.100 --> 00:00:02.740
Jerry,

3
00:00:02.740 --> 00:00:03.840
let you stay by my side.

4
00:00:03.960 --> 00:00:05.480
I said you can do whatever you want.

5
00:00:05.620 --> 00:00:07.200
Isn't that enough?

6
00:00:07.540 --> 00:00:08.780
When will you be obedient?

7
00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:10.680
Always with a man who's so unpredictable,

8
00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:11.800
so quick to violence,

9
00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:12.760
it's terrifying.

10
00:00:13.320 --> 00:00:14.360
How can I sleep?

11
00:00:16.740 --> 00:00:18.200
Fine, since you refuse to,

12
00:00:18.420 --> 00:00:19.960
let's talk business.

13
00:00:20.220 --> 00:00:21.120
What business?

14
00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:28.580
Tell me, did you take the medicine?

15
00:00:30.180 --> 00:00:30.760
Yes.

16
00:00:30.980 --> 00:00:32.200
Why did you do that?

17
00:00:35.040 --> 00:00:36.180
Because I'm only eighteen,

18
00:00:36.700 --> 00:00:37.900
I haven't finished my studies,

19
00:00:38.240 --> 00:00:39.560
I haven't achieved my dreams,

20
00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:40.560
I can't doubt.

21
00:00:41.880 --> 00:00:43.220
That dream you mentioned,

22
00:00:43.380 --> 00:00:44.400
is to paint those dreadful paintings.

